plham

Class Cancel

  • plham.Order
    • plham.Cancel

  • public class Cancel
extends Order
    A cancel request of an order.

    Cancel is performed in terms of Order's agentId and orderId. When a cancel request is accepted, any orders having the agentId and orderId will be cancelled. To be cancelleable, the orderId must be > 0 (which is 0 by default). One (Agent) should assign a unique orderId for each order if needed. The cancel behavior when using the same orderId more than once is undefined.
